"uid":119343,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T20:36:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都OK 以為一般災難片但中間飛車個位幾刺激<br />\n仲可以聽到吳彥祖講廣東話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聽到廣東話真係好開心"},{"pid":"49830acff8c43c258a2c29779fe7a4a8ba5b6fe9","tid":433602,"uid":98659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T21:55:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今日睇左 套野好正喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇咩主角威能 成套都幾合乎情理 條女揸車個part型到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  幾條女都好正  個細路女都好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個細路女係咪拍鬼果個<br />\n老豆係斯巴達國王<br />\n個大佬係德軍狙擊人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d17f8a63ba47d7fe4d8f85880d9595b08999864","tid":433602,"uid":10637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T03:30:41.000Z","msg":"個德國妹好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e498c29e4b6e0d59c3c551d8656aa877c11b2d3","tid":433602,"uid":19990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T05:28:52.000Z","msg":"場面唔夠震撼"},{"pid":"c44ceb4299402f598c1f8619dc5cae307d5cee0a","tid":433602,"uid":81113,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T05:46:26.000Z","msg":"垃圾片<br />\n<br />\n兄弟情描述淺薄<br />\n<br />\n父女情更薄<br />\n<br />\n唔覺有咩感動<br />\n<br />\n注意，以下細字劇透<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">[black]副總統仲親自出手...會唔會太on9?<br />\n<br />\n特勤局一隻卒仔突然level up指揮全場？where is the boss?<br />\n<br />\n最後兩分幾鐘你同我用30秒著好太空衣？無重狀態喎？<br />\n<br />\n碎片橫飛，兩條友同個倉都無比子彈一樣既碎片射中？個機率可以有幾低？<br />\n<br />\n[/black]</span><br />\n<br />\n我都唔想劇透太多，但實在不吐不快，浪費我生命同金錢"},{"pid":"7f8b0b5c6c902cf66700dfd4fa1ea966c4f10d60","tid":433602,"uid":21558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T07:06:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>今日睇左 套野好正喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇咩主角威能 成套都幾合乎情理 條女揸車個part型到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  幾條女都好正  個細路女都好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個細路女係咪拍鬼果個<br />\n老豆係斯巴達國王<br />\n個大佬係德軍狙擊人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似係<br />\n我到完場時先發現個細路女係拍Annabelle 既跛妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac6686a759c2210a162c05c76ff3b59bed79afbf","tid":433602,"uid":31990,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T08:15:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>今日睇左 套野好正喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇咩主角威能 成套都幾合乎情理 條女揸車個part型到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  幾條女都好正  個細路女都好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個細路女係咪拍鬼果個<br />\n老豆係斯巴達國王<br />\n個大佬係德軍狙擊人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似係<br />\n我到完場時先發現個細路女係拍Annabelle 既跛妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個o靚妹好好戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0d605f9e2fc597889456d40ede25bcf081ed778","tid":433602,"uid":21558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T09:49:02.000Z","msg":"今日返工去左幾個地鐵站<br />\n離奇地發現原來都有幾多宣傳海報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我突然覺得我要時不時推下呢個post<br />\n等大家好好考慮清楚去唔去睇<img src=\"/asse